name: RAGER - Demo
summary:
Immerse yourself in the adrenaline-fueled excitement of this melee combat rhythm game!

Master weapon of your choice – sword, mace, claws, hammer, axe, your own fists and many more!

The immersive audiovisual experience will keep you on your toes, stunning visuals and spatial audio technology puts you right in heart of the action.

Gear up, warrior, and prepare to show the world what you're made of in the ultimate battle for survival!
